00:17:29,500 --> 00:17:31,340
that they asked Me to arrive little later,

278
00:17:32,340 --> 00:17:35,260
I couldn't go in. It was, people had to push side.

279
00:17:36,580 --> 00:17:38,820
And when My brothers came little later,

280
00:17:39,140 --> 00:17:41,940
they said, "We just didn't know how are we going, to whom."

