00:18:05,020 --> 00:18:13,460
And the Deputee Minister, Deputee Chief Minister was present there.

286
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:17,660
But you won't know they have, you see, just like as you have here,

287
00:18:17,900 --> 00:18:23,060
Peter Shore and all that, they have very important leaders, you see.

288
00:18:24,620 --> 00:18:28,700
Comunist Party, then we have one very extreme party called Shiv Sena,

289
00:18:29,580 --> 00:18:33,020
which is a fanatic party of Shivaji's, fanatic party.

