00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:55,140
[Hindi]

297
00:19:05,260 --> 00:19:09,460
And all these people, extremes, all kinds of extremes,

298
00:19:09,660 --> 00:19:15,380
then all kinds of these leaders, members of the Assembly and all that.

299
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:19,940
some ministers, all have come,

