00:19:50,060 --> 00:19:52,260
That kind of an attitude sure you can't expect here.

307
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:53,260
Of course not.

308
00:19:53,620 --> 00:19:56,540
But you'll be amazed, in India, how many days I've worked, you know.

309
00:19:57,100 --> 00:20:00,580
I started, say in 1970, may. Slowly everything grew.

310
00:20:02,020 --> 00:20:11,260
So, '71, '72, '73, '74, and you see now.

311
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:14,580
Ten years have passed in Sahaja Yoga.

312
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:32,420
Seekers are amazing. And in Bombay, I am there hardly for ten days.

313
00:20:33,140 --> 00:20:35,460
When I'll go, ten days, fifteen days, at the most.

314
00:20:37,980 --> 00:20:39,740
In Delhi about ten, fifteen days.

315
00:20:42,299 --> 00:20:45,820
In Maharashtra I was a month, at the most.

316
00:20:46,740 --> 00:20:47,860
So, you can imagine.

317
00:20:52,700 --> 00:20:54,780
And how many things, I mean not only on this land

318
00:20:54,980 --> 00:20:56,380
that we have Sahaja Yogis,

319
00:20:57,860 --> 00:21:01,220
but that governement has given us land, people have given us land.

320
00:21:02,700 --> 00:21:06,420
So many things have happened in India. And I feel that

321
00:21:06,900 --> 00:21:09,660
India is the place where Sahaja Yoga will be really established.

322
00:21:11,660 --> 00:21:14,740
Besides I would like to be established more in London.

323
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:18,700
But what can we do? How far can we go with these horrible people?

324
00:21:20,540 --> 00:21:21,660
The media is hopeless.

