00:22:01,420 --> 00:22:03,260
He spoke very highly about Sahaja Yoga.

333
00:22:11,060 --> 00:22:12,180
Here, what to do?

334
00:22:15,220 --> 00:22:19,660
Then maybe it needs some, a breakthrough, one or two proeminent people

335
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:22,500
getting Realization, recognizing You Mother.

336
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:26,300
Maybe we need a breakthrough, some, one or two proeminent people,

337
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:28,580
getting Realization and recognizing You.

