00:23:23,620 --> 00:23:29,380
And next day his wife fell from the horse and died.

352
00:23:30,460 --> 00:23:33,580
At eighty, eighty years of age. Imagine this mad woman eighty years.

353
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:37,460
Such a mad modernism.

354
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:39,460
Oh, his nick name is "Bonkers Hogg".

355
00:23:42,700 --> 00:23:43,820
Bonkers.

