00:23:56,140 --> 00:23:57,180
Horrible.

363
00:23:57,380 --> 00:23:58,620
I mean he just said immediately,

364
00:23:58,820 --> 00:24:01,260
without anything in mind, without any humillity.

365
00:24:02,780 --> 00:24:04,540
And dr. Naveen Singh, you know.

366
00:24:05,500 --> 00:24:08,540
He said, "This man is full of ego, Ahamkara".

367
00:24:12,860 --> 00:24:14,260
Just can't do it.

368
00:24:21,780 --> 00:24:23,580
What can you do?

369
00:24:32,260 --> 00:24:34,780
I've cured some very important people like this fellow,

370
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:37,420
this one I've brought.

371
00:24:38,700 --> 00:24:41,140
He talks very highly of Me, you said.

372
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:46,940
That Indian...

373
00:24:48,900 --> 00:24:50,500
Dr. [Athler].

374
00:24:52,020 --> 00:24:53,380
He gave Me a book.

375
00:24:55,980 --> 00:24:58,500
But he said " I am an archetype also." Thank you.

376
00:24:59,380 --> 00:25:03,740
I don't know what all that is.

