00:25:58,540 --> 00:26:00,540
There is no genuineness left in people anymore.

386
00:26:05,660 --> 00:26:07,820
In India you'll be surprised [as well].

387
00:26:09,260 --> 00:26:12,380
Part of it the money we paid, no doubt, we paid part of it.

388
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:17,820
But part of it was given. They gave Me the paper free.

389
00:26:19,420 --> 00:26:21,820
Here was never [unclear] even if they think to Mother.

390
00:26:22,860 --> 00:26:25,180
Printing free. So many things they did free for Me.

391
00:26:25,620 --> 00:26:27,780
All this is Mother's why should She pay.

392
00:26:32,940 --> 00:26:35,500
They have no sense of saintliness left.

393
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:42,380
This horrible thing like,

