00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:03,299
You see, according to Me it's a great progress in England.

397
00:27:04,700 --> 00:27:07,980
Because after all these are not artificial, these are real things.

398
00:27:10,060 --> 00:27:14,940
So real diamonds are rare, isn't it?

