00:27:25,540 --> 00:27:28,100
So I'm overjoyed, whatever it is.

403
00:27:31,900 --> 00:27:34,580
But you people should not feel depressed, at all.

404
00:27:47,580 --> 00:27:49,180
And if you see the other side of it,

405
00:27:49,380 --> 00:27:52,060
lots of things they are doing, like registration.

406
00:27:53,700 --> 00:27:58,540
You see, it is giving such a boost to us, because now Australians,

407
00:27:59,380 --> 00:28:00,100
are so slavish.

408
00:28:00,299 --> 00:28:02,740
They said, "If it is done in England we'll accept it here".

409
00:28:06,220 --> 00:28:08,380
Authonom. No problem.

410
00:28:11,340 --> 00:28:13,700
They'll not question anything, they'll not say anything.

411
00:28:14,020 --> 00:28:15,860
They'll just accept. Can you believe it?

412
00:28:16,340 --> 00:28:18,180
Thing like that.

